overview: On February 26th Game Changer Wrestling present The Coldest Winter live on FITE straight from the Ukranian Culture Center in Los Angeles, CA! The event features the clash between Thunder Rosa and Tony Deppen as well as the first time ever match where Blake Christian takes on Mike Bailey.  Also in the lineup:  Mascara Dorada vs Gringo Loco Willie Mack vs Jack Alex Zayne vs Jimmy Lloyd Diamond Sheik vs Jordan Oliver Mance Warner Returns  ....and more
title: GCW The Coldest Winter
